16
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:55,100
I never expected that us, father and son, would finally meet each other.

17
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:02,900
Ying Yuan. You're incomparably powerful.

18
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:06,600
Why didn't you make good use of my Asura blood?

19
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:09,200
By that, you can overturn the Three Realms and rule over all sentient beings.

20
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:11,600
As well as restore the Asura Clan.

21
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:14,000
You've traveled back in time hundreds of times.

22
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:20,300
Yet the first thing you say when you were awakened is about your ambition to rule the world and the past.

23
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:23,000
Have you still not figured it out?

24
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,200
You're an exact duplicate of me in terms of appearance.

25
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:28,800
However, your personality resembles your mother's.

26
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:32,600
We, the members of the Asura Clan, are born with divine power,

27
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:35,100
and our cultivation base is a hundred times stronger than other clans'.

28
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:38,500
Yet we're cursed with a short life span.

29
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:43,500
Since Heaven treats us unfairly, then I'll rescue myself at the cost of others' lives.

30
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:49,800
As long as we can live for eternity, I couldn't care less if some weak clans have to be sacrificed.

31
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:54,700
Life and death coexist. Perpetually.

32
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:59,000
The Asura Clan could have lasted for many generations to come.

33
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:04,900
However, due to your ambition, the Asura Clan was attacked by the Six Realms and was annihilated!

34
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,400
This was the consequence of your pursuit for longevity.

35
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:11,200
That was because I fell in love.

36
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:16,300
If I didn't have to save your mother, how could I have failed?

37
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:18,400
How could you have failed?

38
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:25,600
After I witnessed what Huan Qin did, what you did and what others refrain from doing,

39
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:31,200
I finally realized that righteousness can only be achieved by enlightenment, not through cultivation.

40
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:36,300
Only when you let go of the obsession with longevity will you attain a transcendent state.

41
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:38,500
The Deity Clan claims that they're rightful and righteous.

42
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:41,400
But all they want you to do is surrender to the Law of Heaven so that they can remain the ruler!

43
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,700
Why am I born to be inferior to them?

44
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:48,600
The Law of Heaven values equality amongst sentient beings.

45
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:53,000
However you... only think of conquering the world alone.

46
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:07,700
Before Mother perished together with you,

47
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,400
she told you my name.

48
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:16,600
Did you feel a shred of regret at all?

49
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:20,000
You kept using the time and lives you stole to bring Mother back to life.

50
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,400
Because you wanted to indulge yourself in your happiest moment with her.

51
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:29,800
If the meaning of life is longevity, then why did you lose to Mother over and over again?

52
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:35,100
So what even if you possess eternal life, unparalleled cultivation, and overwhelming supremacy?

53
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:37,000
All that's waiting for you...

54
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:42,400
is just everyone you care about perishing for you...

55
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:45,800
leaving only endless loneliness.

56
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:50,600
Finally.

57
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:58,900
Finally... I have a father.

58
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,700
Back then,

59
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:11,000
I always thought I was born a sinner.

60
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:15,600
But when I saw your past with Mother,

61
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,600
I finally knew

62
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:25,000
that I was born because of love.

63
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:30,300
And this love surpassed your ambition and longing for power.

64
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,800
Which is why I can stand before you now.

65
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,600
Mother killed you with my blood.

66
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:41,200
But that wasn't because she truly hated you.

67
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:45,400
She died to save others...

68
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,400
While I was born to save others.

69
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:52,100
You are the one who gave me the opportunity

70
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:57,800
to become the person... who can bring this endless cycle to an end.

71
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:05,300
Let it go, Father.

72
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:10,300
Living an endless life isn't the meaning of life.

73
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:14,300
Only when there is a limit... an end...

74
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,600
will we develop an attachment

75
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,800
and learn to cherish what matters to us.

76
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,700
My son.

77
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:44,000
My good son.

78
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:53,600
All of the mania came from my resentment.

79
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:02,600
It turns out I attained longevity a long time ago.

80
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:18,000
I've always... been living inside the heart of the one I love.

81
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,200
Xuan Ye.

82
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,800
Yuan'er.

83
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,900
Ran Qing.

84
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:23,800
Is it true that you don't hate me?

85
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:26,200
I've never hated you.

86
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:39,100
Yuan'er. Thank you.

87
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,300
My son.

88
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:53,800
Everyone will be parted by death eventually.

89
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,000
My dearest son.

90
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:01,400
Farewell.

91
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:05,400
Mother. Father.

92
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:11,000
In our next life...

93
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:24,400
In our next life... we'll still be family.

94
00:11:13,780 --> 00:11:15,480
My son.

95
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:21,020
This is our farewell.

96
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:52,460
Even if you've overcome the evil inside you, so what?

97
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:58,180
The Asura blood in your body is doomed to bring catastrophe to the Three Realms.

98
00:11:58,180 --> 00:12:03,380
Ying Yuan. You can never escape from this destiny.

99
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:20,228
Now that the barrier that used to divide the Heaven Realm and the Devil Realm no longer exists.

100
00:13:20,228 --> 00:13:25,260
I'd like to see what choice you decide to make.

101
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:32,880
Are you going to stay in the Illusion of Devils and keep trying to kill me

102
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:37,400
or go to protect the sentient beings of the Three Realms that you care so much about?

103
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:07,380
 The Asura King summons thunder strikes from the universe. 

104
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:11,860
 The arrival of Eternal Darkness manifests my power! 

105
00:14:40,740 --> 00:14:46,480
Today, you... will die by my hand!

106
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:50,600
As for the Three Realms... I will also protect it!

107
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:41,420
The Illusion of Devils will weaken without the power of Devil King,

108
00:15:41,420 --> 00:15:46,040
if we keep on launching spells here it will only tear it apart.

109
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:47,680
Do you want to die here?

110
00:15:47,680 --> 00:15:51,800
I definitely won't let you leave the Illusion of Devils. Don't even think about it!

111
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:59,040
The more you want to take me down with you, the more I won't let that happen!

112
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:35,120
- Ying Yuan.
- Ying Yuan.

113
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:47,600
Yan Dan. Yan Dan!

114
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,200
I'm fine.

115
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:11,780
Why did you come in here?

116
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:14,320
I told you before we would stick together in life and death!

117
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:16,660
With our help, we might stand a chance to win.

118
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:20,800
Block Huan Qin's way! We must leave before the entrance disappears!

119
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:29,420
I have no regrets now that I've fought alongside the Three Emperors.

120
00:17:29,420 --> 00:17:31,220
And I'm very happy to have been your friend.

121
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:32,640
Huan Qin is no match for you.

122
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:35,740
Why must you sacrifice your life here?

123
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:38,380
My Asura blood has been awakened.

124
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:43,160
Without the primordial spirit of His Supreme Majesty suppressing it, I can't predict what will happen!

125
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:47,320
Perishing with the Illusion of Devils is the best choice for me.

126
00:17:47,320 --> 00:17:50,160
What about me? Are you going to abandon me again?

127
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:52,000
I'm sorry, Yan Dan.

128
00:17:53,140 --> 00:17:56,820
Yu Mo. Take her and leave!

129
00:17:58,800 --> 00:17:59,840
I won't leave!

130
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,560
Yan Dan. Hurry, go!

131
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:05,140
Yu Mo. Leave now!

132
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:06,760
Go!

133
00:18:20,250 --> 00:18:22,760
- Ying Yuan!
- Yan Dan!

134
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:30,800
Yan Dan!

135
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:34,340
Yu Mo. I'm sorry.

136
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:36,020
Please forget me.

137
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:37,640
Yan Dan!

138
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,960
You're merely a flower demon.

139
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:42,580
You're like a bug going up against a cart.

140
00:19:42,580 --> 00:19:45,060
If you want to live, then you better leave now.

141
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:48,780
Otherwise, I'll make you disappear right now.

142
00:19:48,780 --> 00:19:52,420
Clans and ability have never mattered when you're protecting the ones you love.

143
00:19:52,420 --> 00:19:53,980
Evil can never overpower righteousness.

144
00:19:53,980 --> 00:19:57,840
Regardless how good your schemes or great your spiritual power,

145
00:19:57,840 --> 00:20:01,440
you would never have imagined that you would be defeated by a Four-leaf Lotus!

146
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:05,560
Today, I'll personally avenge my sister!

147
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:07,100
Why didn't you leave?

148
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:11,680
You protect the Three Realms, so let me protect you.

149
00:21:56,980 --> 00:22:02,360
In the past, all we would see is the other's back walking away.

150
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:04,500
But this time...

151
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:11,240
we'll never be apart again.

152
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:24,020
All right.

153
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:28,100
This life was enough.

154
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:34,020
Not even death can pull us apart.

155
00:23:16,060 --> 00:23:19,120
 Congratulations on your triumph, Your Supreme Majesty. 

156
00:23:41,860 --> 00:23:43,300
Both of you...

157
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:48,500
made it back alive.

158
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:58,800
We, Team One Good Deed A Day, is invincible indeed.

159
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:18,300
Come.

160
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:28,360
Your Supreme Majesty, the barrier set by the Primordial Lord has been broken.

161
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,880
The Asura Army of the Dead is on its way to attack the Three Realms.

162
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,860
Marshal Huo De is protecting the Heaven Realm.

163
00:24:32,860 --> 00:24:35,420
However, the other two realms are weak.

164
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:40,080
Your Supreme Majesty, please decide how to deploy the rest of the heavenly army.

165
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:43,280
You and Yu Mo go back first.

166
00:24:43,280 --> 00:24:45,860
After everything is over, I'll come find you.

167
00:24:45,860 --> 00:24:48,860
No. I'll stay to help.

168
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:52,300
Yu Mo. You should go back to Yelan Mountain first.

169
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:55,060
If catastrophe hits the Three Realms, the demons in the mountain will need you.

170
00:24:55,060 --> 00:24:56,700
Yan Dan.

171
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:02,400
If there's danger, call me at any time.

172
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:07,920
You two must return safe and sound.

173
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:20,600
What is it?

174
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:22,320
Your Supreme Majesty.

175
00:25:28,620 --> 00:25:31,840
This is bad. He must be struggling to control the Asura blood inside him.

176
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:34,660
We must figure out a way to suppress it then!

177
00:25:52,420 --> 00:25:54,300
- His Supreme Majesty has been possessed by evil! 
 - Ying Yuan!

178
00:25:54,300 --> 00:25:56,320
Yan Dan! Don't move!

179
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:59,440
If this keeps going, you'll be completely destroyed.

180
00:26:12,660 --> 00:26:14,260
Yan Dan!

181
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:33,720
Ying Yuan. I'm Yan Dan...

182
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:36,160
I'm Yan Dan!

183
00:26:54,780 --> 00:26:59,140
Ying Yuan. I'm Yan Dan.

184
00:26:59,140 --> 00:27:01,920
Open your eyes.

185
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:05,120
Look at me carefully.

186
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:07,880
I'm begging you. Don't let it take over.

187
00:27:08,360 --> 00:27:11,680
No matter whether we're in the Heaven Realm or the Mortal Realm,

188
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:15,900
whether you're Tang Zhou or Ying Yuan, you won't forget me.

189
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:25,840
After the war ended,

190
00:27:27,540 --> 00:27:29,940
didn't we promise each other

191
00:27:29,940 --> 00:27:34,660
that we would be carefree and travel around the world?

192
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:36,340
Ying Yuan...

193
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:40,600
My whole heart is inside you.

194
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:44,720
I'm begging you, don't let it consume you.

195
00:27:45,260 --> 00:27:48,160
I'm begging you, don't forget me.

196
00:27:48,820 --> 00:27:51,260
I begging you. Look at me.

197
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:56,240
Don't let it take over you.

198
00:27:57,580 --> 00:27:59,760
I'm begging you...

