♫   In my dream, the one I loved is with me   ♫

211
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:11,200
♫   The mortal life is short yet we suffered for love with lovers not living up to expectations   ♫

212
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:18,120
♫   A beautiful night can be barren but yet it sees my hatred is full to the brim   ♫

213
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:25,200
♫   As the wind blows and flowers bloom, I could not forget what I'm supposed to   ♫

214
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:31,440
♫   Those who found each other should not be forced to separate   ♫

215
00:30:32,220 --> 00:30:39,440
♫   A lifetime of heartfelt feelings is mistakenly turned into a lies like a cloak in winter   ♫

216
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:46,380
♫   Fate has us spending thousands of years missing each other even if the world ends   ♫

217
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:50,460
♫   From now on, I will have my sorrow and joy in life be my companions   ♫

