00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:33,400
Yan Dan... you're hurt.

228
00:31:35,020 --> 00:31:37,220
You remember me.

229
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:39,440
You remembered me.

230
00:31:40,140 --> 00:31:42,400
I'm fine.

231
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:49,090
I told you before. Let me protect you. As long as you remember me.

232
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:52,340
As long as you stay with me forever.

233
00:31:56,080 --> 00:32:02,280
