234
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:04,480
From the beginning...

235
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:09,500
my love for you has never changed.

236
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:20,140
♫   When the lotus blossoms again, you and I will be together   ♫

237
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:25,140
I'm sorry.

